Class State

  • java.lang.Object
    • State

  • public class State
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores State information from input .csv file. Gets and sets stateData fed in from Project1 class. Includes proper String formatting and String to integer conversion from stateData. Add method for adding State objects to State[]. Print method for printing individual state data from search algorithm, along with a comparison method for comparing state names from Project1.
    Version:
    2/26/17
    Author:
    Stephen Hartman
